{
  "stem": "17625.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- I was in-- in a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what is [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A-- a-- a place with a cook, where people went there every there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rabbi take-- took care of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the reason was, my father was known to-- to rabbi's son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The son-in-law was-- was a-- was a son of-- of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was-- was a-- was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you know what it means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took me to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I didn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had boys in Chrzanów from the yeshiva, which they ate by us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, one, one-- another day, another one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the most customary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I knew a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I should tell you, if I take now the Chrzanów book, and I look up the people there, I didn't-- I didn't-- I didn't-- I didn't know many of them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew more-- more in my-- in my capacity where they were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, for example, organizations, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- there was a-- one was a Poliziani.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- one was a social-- a Bund, and this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't belong there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I belonged more to the-- to the Haggadah, to the more religious ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now, from this point, you went to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your father is helping you in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he helped me out, and I should-- I should be able to stay there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
